data.description: This Beautiful Banning Lewis Ranch home is a Ranch-Style home with Six Beautiful Archways on the Main Level and 9' Ceilings throughout! The many highlights include: Spacious Rooms, Open Floor Layout, an Arched Decorative Wall leading to Basement, All Floors have Luxury Vinyl, Bedrooms have Custom-Made Plantation Shutters, Staggered Kitchen Cabinets with Crown Molding, Recessed Lighting, a Full-Home ADT Security System with RING Doorbell, hookup for Hot Tub, Automatic Coverings for the Kitchen Window and Dining Room Patio Door; and a Fully Fenced and Landscaped Backyard. Enjoy Colorado living in your comfortable backyard Patio with Pergola and a huge Stamped-Concrete patio that is the full width of your home.     In addition, the Main Level offers: Living Room with a Fireplace, Dining Room with a Doggie Door and Backyard access, Kitchen with many Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances and a Pantry, Large Master Suite with a 5-piece Bath and Walk-In Closet, One Additional Bedroom, Full Bath, Large Entranceway and Laundry Room. The Fully Finished Basement has a huge Family Room for many activities, two additional Bedrooms, a Full Bath and Large Storage Area.     Additionally there are automatic sprinklers.     The Banning Lewis Ranch Community has numerous amenities, including neighborhood schools, over 75 acres of Parks/Trails/Open Space, Tennis Courts, Pickle Ball Courts, Basketball Court, Rock Climbing Parks, Zip-Lines, Access to Pools, Splash Pad, Water Park, and Dog Park. Recreation Center has a Clubhouse, Fitness Center, and hosts Classes and Events for all ages. This Community also hosts neighborhood Concerts, Festivals, Food Trucks, Farmers Market and other community events. HOA also provides snow and trash removal. Easy access to Powers Blvd, Marksheffel Rd, and Highway 24 for Entertainment, Restaurants, Shopping and more. Hurry! This home won't last long!
